256
00:20:35,332 --> 00:20:37,332
空高く
High in the sky,

257
00:20:37,332 --> 00:20:41,032
果てしなく
and boundlessly,

258
00:20:41,032 --> 00:20:44,232
抱きしめた未来が
the future I embraced

259
00:20:44,232 --> 00:20:46,532
奇跡になる
becomes a miracle.

260
00:20:46,532 --> 00:20:48,532
生まれた
These born

261
00:20:48,532 --> 00:20:51,532
思いが
feelings

262
00:20:51,532 --> 00:20:54,632
明日へと導くよ
will lead the way to tomorrow.

263
00:20:54,632 --> 00:20:57,132
私だけの光
A light that's mine alone,

264
00:20:57,132 --> 00:21:00,432
放ちたい
I want to set it free.

265
00:21:00,432 --> 00:21:10,032
WOW WOW WOW...

